---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import CallButton from '../components/CallButton.astro';

const siteUrl = 'https://windshieldreplacementlubbock.com';
---

<Layout
  title="About Us | Lubbock Windshield Replacement"
  description="Learn about Lubbock Windshield Replacement — a local auto glass service trusted by Lubbock, TX drivers. Call (806) 450-8900 for same-day service."
  canonical={`${siteUrl}/about/`}
>
  <script slot="head" type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": `${siteUrl}/`},
      {"@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "About", "item": `${siteUrl}/about/`}
    ]
  })} />
  <Header />

  <section style="background-color: #1e3a8a;" class="text-white py-12 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold mb-3">About Lubbock Windshield Replacement</h1>
      <p class="text-blue-200 text-lg max-w-2xl">A local auto glass service that knows West Texas — the roads, the weather, and the vehicles that drive them every day.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Built for the South Plains</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Lubbock is its own world. The wide open skies, the relentless West Texas wind, the way a dust storm can come out of nowhere and blanket the whole city in minutes. The hailstorms that show up every spring with a vengeance, leaving neighborhoods across Tech Terrace, South Overton, and Arnett Benson dealing with dented hoods and cracked windshields all at once. The agricultural trucks that have been running Highway 87 and Loop 289 since before most of us were born, kicking up gravel like it's nothing.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        We know all of this because we operate right here. We're not a call center in another state routing your call to some distant contractor. When you call us, you're reaching people who understand what it's like to drive in Lubbock — who've seen what a bad hail season does to a block of cars near South Plains Mall, and who know how fast a chip turns into a crack when it's 105 degrees in August.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        That local knowledge shapes how we operate: quickly, honestly, and with an understanding of what Lubbock drivers actually deal with.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">What Drives Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        A cracked windshield is an inconvenience. But it's also a safety issue. A compromised windshield weakens the structural integrity of your vehicle's roof. It can distort your field of vision at exactly the wrong moment. In Texas, driving with a cracked windshield that obstructs your view is also a traffic violation — another problem you don't need.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our job is to make fixing your windshield as easy as possible. That means coming to you instead of making you come to a shop. It means handling your insurance claim so you don't have to sit on hold. It means giving you a real price upfront, doing the job right, and getting out of your way so you can get on with your day.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        We work on everything from the F-150s and Silverados that are basically a Lubbock uniform, to the Texas Tech students' sedans and compacts, to the commercial vans and work trucks that keep the West Texas economy running. Every vehicle gets the same quality of work.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10 bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Our Commitments to You</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg" style="color: #dc2626; min-width: 1.5rem;">&#10003;</span>
          <div><strong>Honest assessments.</strong> We'll tell you if your windshield needs replacement or if a simple repair will do. We don't push unnecessary work.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg" style="color: #dc2626; min-width: 1.5rem;">&#10003;</span>
          <div><strong>Upfront pricing.</strong> You get a quote before we start. No surprise charges when the job is done.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg" style="color: #dc2626; min-width: 1.5rem;">&#10003;</span>
          <div><strong>Quality materials.</strong> We use OEM-equivalent glass and professional-grade materials that meet safety standards — not cheap imports.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg" style="color: #dc2626; min-width: 1.5rem;">&#10003;</span>
          <div><strong>Respect for your time.</strong> We show up when we say we will. We complete jobs efficiently. We clean up after ourselves.</div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="font-bold text-lg" style="color: #dc2626; min-width: 1.5rem;">&#10003;</span>
          <div><strong>Insurance expertise.</strong> We know the ins and outs of getting glass claims approved and will handle all contact with your insurer.</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Serving All of Lubbock</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
        Our mobile service covers every part of Lubbock — Heart of Lubbock, Tech Terrace, Maxey Park, Clapp Park, North Overton, South Overton, Stubbs-Stewart, Bayless-Atkins, Wheelock, Monterey, Arnett Benson, and everywhere else in the city. We also extend service to Wolfforth, Shallowater, Idalou, Ransom Canyon, Slaton, New Deal, and Abernathy.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Whether you're a Texas Tech student on a tight budget trying to figure out if insurance will cover your chip, a homeowner in South Overton dealing with hail aftermath, or a business owner who needs a fleet vehicle back on the road fast — we're here to help.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="text-center py-10 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1e3a8a;">Ready to Work With Us?</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-5 max-w-xl mx-auto">Give us a call. We'll assess your windshield damage, check your insurance, and get you scheduled — fast.</p>
      <CallButton label="Call (806) 450-8900 Today" size="lg" center={true} />
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-3">Available 24/7 for emergency service</p>
    </div>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
